title: Watch case

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a watch case, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front perspective view of a watch case;
FIG. 2 is a front view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a rear view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 4 is a left side view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 5 is a right side view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 6 is a top view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 7 is a bottom view of the watch case shown in FIG. 1.
The broken line showing of the watch hands and internal mechanism are for illustrative purposes and form no part of the claimed design.
